CustomField.description: If this field is set, it overrides the Practice to which a Misc Adjustment's Transactions will roll up for Practice Actuals, even if its Project is in a different Practice. Typically a Misc Adjustment's Transactions roll up to its Project's Practice. Note that either way, the Transactions will continue to roll up to the same Project's Project Actuals.

CustomField.label: Override Project Practice
